m_{\ell \to \ell+1} = \left( \nabla_{q^{(\ell+1)}} \mathcal{F}^{(\ell+1)}, \pi_{\ell \to \ell+1} \right),

where \pi_{\ell \to \ell+1} is a proof term witnessing: \varphi_\ell(q^{(\ell)}) \implies \varphi_{\ell+1}(q^{(\ell+1)}_{\text{updated}}).

