\{V(q_0) \leq r\} \ \text{system} \ \{V(q_t) \leq e^{-\alpha t}r + \beta/\alpha + \gamma\delta\},

with machine-checkable proof of the Hoare triple, where \gamma = \sup_{q} \| \frac{\partial V}{\partial q} \|.

