Appendix B: Enriched Category Theory – Additional Lemmas

Lemma B.1 (Enriched Yoneda for Beliefs). For a \mathcal{V}-enriched category \mathcal{B}_\mathcal{V}, the Yoneda embedding Y: \mathcal{B}_\mathcal{V} \to [\mathcal{B}_\mathcal{V}^{\text{op}}, \mathcal{V}] given by Y(B) = \mathcal{B}_\mathcal{V}(-,B) is a metric-preserving functor when \mathcal{B}_\mathcal{V} is equipped with the enriched structure and the functor category is given the pointwise hom-object. In particular, for any objects B, B',

